{"tid":1948952,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國：全球數周內恐糧食短缺 多地鎖國擾亂供應鏈 稻麥價格急漲","createTime":"2020-03-29T10:30:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T11:56:42.000Z","uid":11454,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"107ef0bec2b05dba65a41fb1d88bd3ee0f0098e1","tid":1948952,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"&laquo; 返回前頁<br />\n文章： <br />\n<br />\n2020年3月27日<br />\n<br />\n聯合國：全球數周內恐糧食短缺<br />\n多地鎖國擾亂供應鏈 稻麥價格急漲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放大圖片 / 顯示原圖<br />\n疫情在全球蔓延，多國實施禁令限制民眾外出，要在家避疫，導致食物及日常用品出現搶購潮，農場勞工短缺，食品供應鏈遭打斷；加上部分國家為保障食物及物資供應充裕，實施保護主義，聯合國糧食及農業組織（FAO）警告，最快未來數周全球面臨糧食短缺。 聯合國糧農組織首席經濟師托蘭洛（Maximo Torero）表示 ...<br />\n（節錄）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/international/article/2416199/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%95%B8%E5%91%A8%E5%85%A7%E6%81%90%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkej.com%2Fdailynews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F2416199%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E5%2590%2588%25E5%259C%258B%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2581%2590%25E7%25B3%25A7%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%259F%25AD%25E7%25BC%25BA&d=XV0%2F%2BsWk6HIEEz5%2BsPHJe0kSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=33241296\" target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkej.com/dailynews/international/article/2416199/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%EF%BC%9A%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%95%B8%E5%91%A8%E5%85%A7%E6%81%90%E7%B3%A7%E9%A3%9F%E7%9F%AD%E7%BC%BA</a>"},{"pid":"559d554dce1dfd1e5e41a4d4be5e1ef432bafa0f","tid":1948952,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-29T10:31:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddd5c8e0319fc0ff3de04da9ed9a8427d33416a","tid":1948952,"uid":321837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedB